  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NumberExpression, Observable, Property<Number>, ReadOnlyProperty<Number>, ObservableIntegerValue, ObservableNumberValue, ObservableValue<Number>, WritableIntegerValue, WritableNumberValue, WritableValue<Number>, StyleableProperty<Number>

    public class SimpleStyleableIntegerProperty
extends StyleableIntegerProperty
    This class extends SimpleIntegerProperty and provides a full implementation of a StyleableProperty. This class is used to make a IntegerProperty, that would otherwise be implemented as a SimpleIntegerProperty, style‑able by CSS.
    Since:
    JavaFX 8.0
    See Also:
    SimpleIntegerProperty, CssMetaData, StyleableProperty, StyleableIntegerProperty
